Memory map..
- assume 240x240 * 8bit == 57600/screen
- assume dual buffer == 57600*2 == 115200/pair
- leaving 12K for other
12k splits up into..
- RAM (8k?)
- buffer pointer
- sprite list?
- audio buffer?
- command queue to GPU
- response queue from GPU


Desired features..

cpu1:
